{"title":"基于Hexo+git搭建个人博客","uid":"73557fa6b66c655776f5051b7a73b32a","slug":"hexo-blog-github","date":"2023-03-09T08:49:04.000Z","updated":"2023-03-10T01:50:05.784Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hexo-blog-github.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>欢迎来到我的博客，本篇主要介绍Mac如何基于Hexo+git搭建自己的博客站。</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"什么是-Hexo？\"><a href=\"#什么是-Hexo？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是 Hexo？\"></a>什么是 Hexo？</h3><p>Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。Hexo 使用 Markdown（或其他渲染引擎）解析文章，在几秒内，即可利用靓丽的主题生成静态网页。</p>\n<h3 id=\"安装Hexo前的环境\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo前的环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo前的环境\"></a>安装Hexo前的环境</h3><ul>\n<li><p>Node.js (Node.js 版本需不低于 10.13，建议使用 Node.js 12.0 及以上版本)</p>\n<p>  使用<code>Homebrew</code>或者<code>nvm</code>来安装 node 环境，建议使用<code>nvm</code>来安装 node，便于以后可以切换 node 版本</p>\n<h4 id=\"brew-安装-node\"><a href=\"#brew-安装-node\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"#brew 安装 node:\"></a>#brew 安装 node:</h4>  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">brew update  &#x2F;&#x2F;先更新brew\n\nbrew install node &#x2F;&#x2F;安装最新版\nbrew install node@版本号 &#x2F;&#x2F;指定版本\n\nnode -v &#x2F;&#x2F;查看当前版号</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"nvm-安装-node\"><a href=\"#nvm-安装-node\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"#nvm 安装 node:\"></a>#nvm 安装 node:</h4><ol>\n<li><p>如果未安装<code>nvm</code>执行brew进行安装：</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">brew update\nbrew install nvm\nnvm -v &#x2F;&#x2F;查看版本</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>配置所需的环境变量：</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">vim ~&#x2F;.bash_profile</code></pre>\n<p>  在 <code>~/.bash_profile</code> 中添加以下几行环境变量：</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">export NVM_DIR&#x3D;~&#x2F;.nvm\nsource $(brew --prefix nvm)&#x2F;nvm.sh</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>按键盘 ESC 后输入 <code>:wq</code> 保存并关闭你的文件。 使用以下命令让该变量在shell环境中生效，在下一次打开终端，它将自动加载。</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">source ~&#x2F;.bash_profile</code></pre>\n</li>\n<li><p>使用nvm进行安装node:</p>\n  <pre class=\"line-numbers language-none\"><code class=\"language-none\">nvm install node  &#x2F;&#x2F;安装最新稳定版\nnvm install node v14.10.0 &#x2F;&#x2F;安装指定版本\n\nnvm list &#x2F;&#x2F;查看已装node列表\nnvm use v14.10.0  &#x2F;&#x2F;切换当前版本\n\nnode -v &#x2F;&#x2F;查看版本切换是否成功\nnpm -v &#x2F;&#x2F;查看版本切换是否成功</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>Git</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装Hexo\"><a href=\"#安装Hexo\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装Hexo\"></a>安装Hexo</h3>","feature":true,"text":" 欢迎来到我的博客，本篇主要介绍Mac如何基于Hexo+git搭建自己的博客站。 什么是 Hexo？Hexo 是一个快速、简洁且高效的博客框架。Hexo 使用 Markdown（或其他渲染引擎）解析文章，在几秒内，即可利用靓丽的主题生成静态网页。 安装Hexo前的环境 Node....","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":991,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Hexo.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Blog","slug":"Blog","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Blog.json"},{"name":"Hexo","slug":"Hexo","count":1,"path":"api/tags/Hexo.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF-Hexo%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">什么是 Hexo？</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo%E5%89%8D%E7%9A%84%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装Hexo前的环境</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#brew-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-node\"><span class=\"toc-text\">#brew 安装 node:</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#nvm-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85-node\"><span class=\"toc-text\">#nvm 安装 node:</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85Hexo\"><span class=\"toc-text\">安装Hexo</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"微风Harvey","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/img/IMG_logo.JPG","link":"/","description":"","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"markdown-语法练习","uid":"f72bf75547cde41b2e233f0b03b51710","slug":"markdown-exercises","date":"2023-03-09T09:10:19.000Z","updated":"2023-03-10T01:50:05.784Z","comments":true,"path":"